Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.19,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3B343F&\4c&H3B343F&}平家の武士が
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.90,CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}竟有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.90,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}何という…
