Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.46,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}すまぬな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3B343F&\4c&H3B343F&}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.96,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3B343F&\4c&H3B343F&}すまぬ
