Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.76,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3B343F&\4c&H3B343F&}おとうみたいに殺せ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.40,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H362C2C&\4c&H362C2C&}这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.40,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H362C2C&\4c&H362C2C&}これはこれは
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.02,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H362C2C&\4c&H362C2C&}可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.02,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H362C2C&\4c&H362C2C&}なんと　まあ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.07,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}有跳蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.07,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}蚤が
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.07,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}还有虱子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.07,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}虱もおります
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.65,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}真的要让这孩子住进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.65,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}本当にこの子を屋敷に置くのでございますか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.99,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}要让他住进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.99,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B4056&\4c&H1B4056&}ございますか
